017package org.apache.juneau.plaintext;
018
019import org.apache.juneau.*;
020import org.apache.juneau.plaintext.annotation.*;
021
022/**
023 * Metadata on classes specific to the PlainText serializers and parsers pulled from the {@link PlainText @PlainText} annotation on
024 * the class.
025 *
026 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
027
028 * </ul>
029 */
030public class PlainTextClassMeta extends ExtendedClassMeta {
031
032   /**
033    * Constructor.
034    *
035    * @param cm The class that this annotation is defined on.
036    * @param mp PlainText metadata provider (for finding information about other artifacts).
037    */
038   public PlainTextClassMeta(ClassMeta<?> cm, PlainTextMetaProvider mp) {
039      super(cm);
040   }
041}
